# -----------------
 Compiling 8051-Assembler Sources

 All 8051-type Assembler Sources can be compiled using
 the Macroassembler AS written by Alfred Arnold.
 This Macroassembler is available as GNU GPL source code.
 http://john.ccac.rwth-aachen.de:8000/as/

 File specific build informations can be found in the
 header of each assembler file.

# -----------------
 PCB and Hardware Layout

 Schematics and PCB files are provided for
 CadSoft EAGLE Light which is available as freeware.
 http://www.cadsoft.de/freeware.htm

 Schematic and PCB file formats may change in the future
 in favor for open source alternative with non-proprietary file formats.
